<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <h2>なぜ 7/16 なのか</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid stagger-children">
      <div class="feature-card reveal" style="--i: 0;">
        <div class="card-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17.94 17.94A10.07 10.07 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.45 18.45 0 0 1 5.06-5.94" />
              <path d="M9.9 4.24A9.12 9.12 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19" />
              <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">匿名性</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">投稿者がわからない。リアクションした瞬間、あなたの正体が明かされる。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal" style="--i: 1;">
        <div class="card-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="16 3 21 3 21 8" />
              <line x1="4" y1="20" x2="21" y2="3" />
              <polyline points="21 16 21 21 16 21" />
              <line x1="15" y1="15" x2="21" y2="21" />
              <line x1="4" y1="4" x2="9" y2="9" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">偶然性</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">16枚から7枚をランダム抽出。何が共有されるかは運命次第。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal" style="--i: 2;">
        <div class="card-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">7日間のリチュアル</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">1日1枚。毎日のサプライズが友達との新しい会話を生む。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal" style="--i: 3;">
        <div class="card-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">プライベート</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">友達限定の空間。知らない人には届かない、安心の写真共有。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background: var(--gray-950);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  /* Card with animated gradient border */
  .feature-card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 1px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    transition: background 0.5s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: conic-gradient(
      from var(--gradient-angle),
      rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3),
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1),
      rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05),
      rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1),
      rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3)
    );
    animation: gradientRotate 3s linear infinite;
  }

  .card-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 20px;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .card-glow {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-inner {
    background: var(--gray-950);
    border-radius: 19px;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .feature-icon-wrap {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08);
    color: var(--purple-light);
    transition: background 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-icon-wrap {
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
